{"tid":132642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟D人點撚樣日日用踎廁","createTime":"2017-02-24T03:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T07:21:04.000Z","uid":69279,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68e1af8fa92cea704e27bfd97c86c783a049a432","tid":132642,"uid":69279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:38:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的。<br />\n<br />\n小弟因公出trip去大陸一個星期，咁我日日朝早都慣左食完早餐就要痾屎。而大陸果邊個個office，係 無 坐 廁 的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟焗住日日用個死人踎廁痾屎，平時無乜野最多我一分鐘解決當練腳，今日個肚唔係幾舒服，就踎多左幾分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母真係好撚攰，原本已經肚痛到仆街，踎o係度對腳震下震下，D腸又攪下攪下，真係好撚辛苦。到痾完企起身，對腳完全係痺曬好似針拮咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係辛苦過平時做gym練腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟日日用踎廁啲人做gym係唔係就可以skip leg day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係一定要腳力去到咁上下先用到踎廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0568fb600f4f65762fe10bd8c40a6316c08ec2","tid":132642,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:41:38.000Z","msg":"幻想下你琴晚攸gym操完腳, 今朝再用踎廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc18e7222b5724499100e8ca0af4d3177683add","tid":132642,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"踎係度痾屎係健康d架，個姿勢可以痾哂d屎出黎"},{"pid":"a916f8f9bbbd3bb723865be54f02f8c37f2bd9fe","tid":132642,"uid":39317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"大陸人乾淨又企理<br />\n平時痾完D屎尿滴返少少落廁板 <br />\n真係想爭櫈仔咁坐落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4abdeb2eb6b1edeb67485734f994dbdcf510e4","tid":132642,"uid":3465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"渣ga"}]}